USE CASE: 15 produce a population report containing the following columns: 

The name of the continent/region/country.
The total population of the continent/region/country.
The total population of the continent/region/country living in cities (including a %).
The total population of the continent/region/country not living in cities (including a %)

CHARACTERISTIC INFORMATION
Goal in Context
As an organisation, I would like to be able to produce a report as mentioned above

Scope
Company.

Level
Primary task.

Preconditions
Database contains appropriate data.

Success End Condition
A report is available for the organisation to analyse.

Failed End Condition
No report is produced.

Primary Actor
Organisation

Trigger
A request for the data is made


EXTENSIONS
None.
SUB-VARIATIONS
None.

SCHEDULE
DUE DATE: Code review 2
